4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that provides a comprehensive education in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and promises to prepare them for a career as a data scientist. The course lasts for 16 weeks and includes classes three times a week with a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion of the course, students receive a recognized certificate. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using powerful libraries such as Python, Pandas, and Numpy. They will also gain experience with algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course emphasizes practical application, teaching students how to tackle real-life challenges and develop their own AI projects. The syllabus and content can be delivered in either English or Spanish, with live classes taught in the language of the student's campus. For more information, visit the website at [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop